Text:
WHO FUCKING CARES!!!!!!!!!!!!!!
WHAT A WASTE!!!!!!!!!!!

First of all, a lot of people care. She isn't one of the most successful female icons in history for no reason. Secondly, how did you end up here if you weren't looking for it? And last, but not least, your excessive use of exclamation points doesn't make you look any less like an idiot. If anything, it makes you look like a complete dumbass.
